Metadata: Third International Conference on Marine Bioinvasions: abstract book
"Third International Conference on Marine Bioinvasions," La Jolla, California, March 16-19, 2003.

The 126 abstracts compiled here from the Third International Conference on Marine Bioinvasions held in March 2003 address topics such as assessment and prediction, routes and factors enabling invasions, species interactions, case studies, issues of jurisdiction, and many more.
